> We use gpt-oss-120b~\cite{gptoss} for the Data Verifier. The detailed prompt is provided **as follows**:

*(然后紧接着放你的 `tcolorbox` 代码块)*

### 选项 2：指代方位（如果 Prompt 在本段下方）
> \textbf{Data Verifier.}
> We use gpt-oss-120b~\cite{gptoss} for the Data Verifier, with the detailed prompt **presented below**.

### 选项 3：指代当前章节
> \textbf{Data Verifier.}
> We use gpt-oss-120b~\cite{gptoss} for the Data Verifier. The detailed evaluation rubric and prompt are provided **in this section**.

